#. js-lingui-id: HP7per
#: src/pages/settings/applications/utils/getStandardApplicationDescription.ts
msgid ""
"The base data model every Twenty workspace runs on.\n"
"\n"
"#### What \"foundation\" means\n"
"\n"
"Every Twenty workspace starts with this set of objects. They define the shape of your CRM, including relationships, activity, and reporting. Everything else, including marketplace apps, AI agents, and custom objects, plugs into them.\n"
"\n"
"#### Included objects\n"
"- **People & Companies**: contact and account records\n"
"- **Opportunities**: your sales pipeline\n"
"- **Notes & Tasks**: activity and follow-ups\n"
"- **Workflows & Dashboards**: automation and reporting\n"
"\n"
"Remove this app and the rest of Twenty has nothing to hang off.\n"
"\n"
"#### Build your own app\n"
"\n"
"Extend Twenty with your own objects, fields, logic functions, or AI skills. Scaffold a new app in one command:\n"
"\n"
"```bash\n"
"npx create-twenty-app@latest my-twenty-app\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"Then inside the folder:\n"
"\n"
"```bash\n"
"cd my-twenty-app\n"
"yarn twenty dev\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"See the [Getting Started guide](https://twenty.com/developers/extend/apps/getting-started) for the full walkthrough, and [Building Apps](https://twenty.com/developers/extend/apps/building) for the `defineApplication` / `defineEntity` APIs."
msgstr ""
"El modelo de datos base sobre el que funciona cada espacio de trabajo de Twenty.\n"
"\n"
"#### Qué significa \"base\"\n"
"\n"
"Todo espacio de trabajo de Twenty comienza con este conjunto de objetos. Definen la forma de tu CRM, incluidas las relaciones, la actividad y los informes. Todo lo demás, incluidas las apps del marketplace, los agentes de IA y los objetos personalizados, se conecta a ellos.\n"
"\n"
"#### Objetos incluidos\n"
"- **Personas y empresas**: registros de contactos y cuentas\n"
"- **Oportunidades**: tu embudo de ventas\n"
"- **Notas y tareas**: actividad y seguimientos\n"
"- **Flujos de trabajo y paneles**: automatización e informes\n"
"\n"
"Quita esta app y el resto de Twenty no tendrá en qué apoyarse.\n"
"\n"
"#### Crea tu propia app\n"
"\n"
"Amplía Twenty con tus propios objetos, campos, funciones de lógica o capacidades de IA. Genera la estructura de una app nueva con un solo comando:\n"
"\n"
"```bash\n"
"npx create-twenty-app@latest my-twenty-app\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"Luego, dentro de la carpeta:\n"
"\n"
"```bash\n"
"cd my-twenty-app\n"
"yarn twenty dev\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"Consulta la [guía de inicio](https://twenty.com/developers/extend/apps/getting-started) para el recorrido completo y [Creación de apps](https://twenty.com/developers/extend/apps/building) para las API de `defineApplication` / `defineEntity`."

